data.description: Beautiful custom home with a private 4.83 acres setting. The home is located in a safe neighborhood surrounded by great neighbors. The house has crown molding, electric cooktop (gas is available), large laundry room, generator, and four bedrooms with their own private bathroom. Inviting entry leads to spacious living area and kitchen with lots of storage. Two porches perfect for good cup of coffee in the morning and family time in the evening.
